summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2007 CADILLAC SRX. THE CONTACT STATED THAT WHILE DRIVING 40 MPH, THE OVERHEAD AIR BAGS DEPLOYED WITHOUT WARNING. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO THE DEALER FOR DIAGNOSIS. THE DEALER STATED THEY DID NOT KNOW WHY THE AIR BAG DEPLOYED. THE MANUFACTURE WAS CONTACTED. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT REPAIRED. THE APPROXIMATE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 151,000. THE VIN WAS NOT AVAILABLE.
